Package: scstruc
Version: 0.99.0
Title: Bayesian network analysis for single-cell transcriptomic data
Authors@R: person("Noriaki", "Sato", email = "nori@hgc.jp", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: The library infers the gene regulatory network based on Bayesian network structure from single-cell transcriptomic data. The package evaluates inferred networks based on causal relationships between genes. Marker arc detection is supported based on metadata.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
